>>HEY THANKS FOR TAKING ME OUT TO LUNCH, MAL.
>>OH, PLEASE, I LOVE SPENDING SMALL AMOUNTS

OF TIME WITH MY SISTER.
>>I'M JUST TRYING TO EAT HEALTHIER, YOU

KNOW?
>>WHY YOU LOOK GREAT!

>>YEAH, I KNOW, BUT I'M JUST SO TIRED
OF GETTING OUT BREATH EVERY TIME I USE THE STAIR

TO MY HOUSE.
>>WELL STAIRS CAN BE HARD.

>>NO STAIR.
THERE'S ONLY ONE.

>>WELL WHIT, THE FAT IN THE SUGAR IS
WHAT MAKES FOOD SO GOOD.

I MEAN HAVE YOU EVER HEARD OF A HEALTHY CHURRO?
>>MAYBE THEY HAVE SOME LOW FAT OPTIONS.

>>HI LADIES MY NAME IS BRODY, I'LL BE
YOUR SERVER TODAY.

CAN I GET YOU STARTED OFF WITH ANYTHING?
>>YEAH DO YOU HAVE ANY LOW FAT OPTIONS HERE?

>>WE DO.
IF YOU LOOK ON THIS SIDE THAT'S OUR SKINNY

DELICIOUS MENU.
HALF THE CALORIES.

>>OH!
>>UM, I THINK I'M JUST GOING TO TAKE A NUMBER

TWO.
>>AND I WILL HAVE THE APPLE BACON BURGER FROM

THE
SKINNY DELICIOUS MENU.

>>GREAT.
>>WHOA, THEY HAVE A HEALTHY BACON BURGER?

>>MHM.
AND I GET TWICE THE SATISFACTION KNOWING THAT

I'M
EATING SOMETHING HEALTHY.

YOU SHOULD TRY IT SOMETIME.
IT'S A RUSH.

>>OH.
>>HOLD ON, DID YOU SAY YOU LIKE SPENDING SMALL

AMOUNTS OF TIME WITH ME?
>>ALL RIGHT HERE IS YOUR BURGER AND FRIES

AND YOUR
APPLE BACON BURGER.

>>THAT WAS SNAPPY.
>>COULD I HAVE YOU STAND OVER HERE?

>>OH YES.
OH LOOK MAL!

LOOKS LIKE MY BURGER IS JUST AS BIG
AS YOURS, BUT HALF THE CALORIES.

DON'T TAKE IT PERSONALLY.
OH WHERE ARE WE GOING?

>>OH JUST STEP UP HERE MAM.
>>WHAT IS THIS?

>>WELL THAT'S THE DELICIOUS
PART OF THE MEAL

AND THIS IS THE SKINNY.
>>WHAT?

THAT'S FALSE ADVERTISING.
>>OH DON'T WORRY.

WE'LL WATCH THOSE CALORIES FOR YOU HERE.
OKAY CAN I GET YOU TWO ANYTHING ELSE TO DRINK?

>>UM, WATER IS FINE FOR ME.
>>OKAY.

>>COULD I HAVE A STRAWBERRY LEMONADE?
>>OH ABSOLUTELY.

YEAH, HERE WE GO.
>>NO!

>>UM, SO.
I DON'T KNOW IF I TOLD YOU BUT, TOM AND

I GOT A DOG.
YEAH WE DEBATED ABOUT IT FOR A WHILE BUT EVENTUALLY

WE JUST
DECIDED TO DO IT YOU KNOW?

>>HERE YOU GO AND I FORGOT TO
BRING OUT YOUR DIPPING SAUCES.

WOULD YOU LIKE KETCHUP OR HONEY MUSTARD?
>>OH, I LOVE HONEY MUSTARD.

>>DO YOU?
THAT'S TOO BAD.

>>WHAT?
NO!

OH!
>>ANYWAY SO WE FINALLY WENT TO THE ANIMAL

SHELTER AND SAID,
WHAT THE HEY!

YOU KNOW?
HE'S SUCH A BLEEDING HEART FOR ANIMALS.

HE JUST REALLY REALLY LOVES ANIMALS.
>>COME ON!

RUN THE COW YOU'RE EATING COULD
RUN FASTER THAN THAT!

>>WHERE DID YOU COME FROM?
>>LET'S GO, LET'S GO!

>>I JUST WANT SOME LEMONADE!
>>THAT'S 200 CALORIES!

CURL!
CURL!

CURL!
>>OW!

OW!
>>COME ON!

>>THAT HURTS.
>>COME ON!

>>SO DO YOU STILL WORK AT THE GAP OR WHAT?
>>ALL RIGHT.

CAN I INTEREST EITHER OF YOU IN
SOME DESSERT TODAY?

>>UM, ACTUALLY THAT PIE LOOKS
REALLY GOOD. WHAT?

>>HEY MAM I'M GOING TO NEED YOU TO
SWALLOW THIS TAPEWORM.

>>WHAT?
NO!
NO!
